Research Log - Project Momo - [Dr. Madretsma, Aug. 25, 2022]
Research Entry: ...Additionally, it has come to our attention that the hybrid, Momo, exhibits an intriguing 
behavioral response, as it appears to be attracted and drawn towards any source of red light,

Research Log - Project Momo - [Dr. Madretsma, May 20, 2023]
Research Entry: It is with great concern that I document the unexpected breach of containment by 
Momo. The security team has notified me of a series of unsettling events that transpired within 
the laboratory, resulting in the escape of the hybrid creature.

Research Log - Project Momo - [Dr. Madretsma, Jan. 17, 2023]
Research Entry: ...In response to the hybrid's inborn tendency to be drawn towards any source of red 
light, I am now requesting the entire laboratory to be repainted in red.

Research Log - Project Momo - [Dr. Madretsma, Dec. 30, 2022]
Research Entry: Through careful observation and analysis, it has become apparent that the process of 
fusing different species' DNA within Momo has resulted in a unique manifestation of 
psychological disorder - schizophrenia.
